"i" "infantry" "marches around and captures things" utype
"a" "armor" "faster than infantry, limited to open terrain" utype
"S" "Special Forces" "Special infiltration units" utype
"A" "Air Lift Plane" "Big cargo plane, for moving supplies and troops" utype
"f" "fighter" "interceptor to get those nasty Aircraft" utype
"h" "chopper" "Helicopter for nailing things on the ground" utype
"b" "bomber" "long range aircraft, carries infantry and bombs" utype
"d" "destroyer" "fast, cheap, and sinks subs" utype
"s" "submarine" "sneaks around and sinks ships" utype
"r" "radar" "needed to see things" utype
"t" "transport ship" "carries units and supplies across the water" utype
"j" "Jeep" "trucks and jeeps for moving infantry and supplies" utype
"X" "Mech Infantry" "Infantry in Powered Armor and AFV's" utype
"C" "carrier" "carries aircraft around" utype
"z" "Spy Plane" "Fast, hard to see spy craft" utype
"B" "Battleship" "the most powerful ship" utype
"G" "missle" "powerful explosive, Very accurate" utype
"N" "atomic" "Nuclear fuel unit, or nuclear bomb" utype
"e" "Engineers" "produces things, fights sieges" utype
"O" "Bolo" "Huge CyberTank.  A veritable land Battleship" utype
"L" "Land Fortification" "For strengthening cities" utype
"/" "Base" "airstrip plus port" utype
"V" "Village" "small town, no airport, produces taxes, can supply infantry" utype
"*" "Town" "smaller than a city, no airport" utype
"@" "City" "capital of a side" utype


